Usage

Use {{Owns device|device_page}} or {{Owns device|device_page|notes}} on your page to add it to the list, e.g {{Owns device|Google_Nexus_5_(lg-hammerhead)|broken screen}}

You may want to purge cache to see changes (near edit button: More->purge cache)

On your userpage you can use {{My devices}} to include there the list of your devices

On device pages {{Device owners}} is available
